sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP SDK
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant ObjStore as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Controller
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(init container)
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(sidecar)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines/upload<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP
    API->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec YAML<br/>HTTP/S 9000/TCP
    API-->>User: Pipeline ID

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Create run record<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP, SA Token
    K8s->>Argo: Workflow event
    Argo->>K8s: Create Driver pod<br/>(init container)

    activate Driver
    Driver->>MLMD: Create execution context<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP
    Driver->>API: Cache lookup<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP
    alt Cache Hit
        Driver-->>Argo: Return cached outputs<br/>Skip Launcher
    else Cache Miss
        Driver->>K8s: Generate pod spec patch<br/>PVC create if needed
        deactivate Driver

        activate Launcher
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP/S 9000/TCP
        Note over Launcher: Execute user container
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP/S 9000/TCP
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP
        deactivate Launcher
    end

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 2: Workflow State Persistence

    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status change<br/>(Informer watch)
    activate PA
    PA->>API: ReportWorkflow<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Bearer Token (projected SA)
    API->>DB: Update run status<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP
    deactivate PA

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 3: Recurring Run Scheduling

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringRuns<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    K8s-->>SWC: ScheduledWorkflow event<br/>(Informer watch)
    activate SWC
    SWC->>SWC: Evaluate cron/periodic schedule
    SWC->>API: CreateRun<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Bearer Token (projected SA)
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    deactivate SWC
